# Docker GUI

Web interface for docker management. Provides statistics for each container, pull and push containers, commits, mount directories, port forwarding, and more.



### Installing

```
git clone https://github.com/vadimoch13/dockerGui.git
cd ./dockerGui
go build
```

### Usage
dockerGui --listen localhost:3000 --auth-login admin --auth-password admin
Open web-browser and go to http://localhost:3000/index

